name: $group
desc: Returns: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify an employer group. May also be referred to as a Policy or Group ID.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify an employer group. May also be referred to as a Policy or Group ID.

name: $groupDisplay
desc: Returns: A short description for the group.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short description for the group.

name: $subGroup
desc: Returns: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subset of an employer group.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subset of an employer group.

name: $subGroupDisplay
desc: Returns: A short description for the subgroup.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short description for the subgroup.

name: $plan
desc: Returns: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a collection of benefits provided to employees. May be referred to as a Section or Division ID.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a collection of benefits provided to employees. May be referred to as a Section or Division ID.

name: $planDisplay
desc: Returns: A short description for the plan.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short description for the plan.

name: $subPlan
desc: Returns: Identifies a sub-style or sub-collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subset of a collection of benefits provided to employees.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies a sub-style or sub-collective of coverage issued by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subset of a collection of benefits provided to employees.

name: $subPlanDisplay
desc: Returns: A short description for the subplan.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short description for the subplan.

name: $class
desc: Returns: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issues by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a class of coverage such as a level of deductables or co-payment.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies a style or collective of coverage issues by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a class of coverage such as a level of deductables or co-payment.

name: $classDisplay
desc: Returns: A short description for the class.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short description for the class.

name: $subClass
desc: Returns: Identifies a sub-style or sub-collective of coverage issues by the underwriter, for example may be used to identify a subclass of coverage such as a sub-level of deductables or co-payment.

pvardefs.name: pValue
